  {
    "task": "Develop a three-tiered response plan",
    "owner": "Jason",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "We have a what we call a three-tiered response plan. Obviously, this is no similar to everyone else right now. We have a mitigate um process which we're currently in now. We then have a restart phase, and then we have a reimagine phase."
  },
  {
    "task": "Conduct one-on-one operator check-ins",
    "owner": "Jason",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "We've been doing one-on-one operator check-ins. We have 240 listed operators with us. So again, these are daily to weekly check-ins by all our teams to make sure everyone's be able to access business advice um and some of the wage support."
  },
  {
    "task": "Redeploy staff into the kiwifruit industry",
    "owner": "Jason",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "We've been um taking some organizations or employers that have maybe at least five to 10 staff members displaced through to Hobbiton who had one of the largest at around 270, and actually redeploying them and offering them redeployment options into the kiwifruit industry."
  },
  {
    "task": "Develop a destination management plan",
    "owner": "Jason",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "We will now be developing a destination management plan and that'll be happening nationally as well to try and what we call transform tourism for the better."
