    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "We are looking to be bolder, more disruptive to enable you to help you transform how you and other Waikato councils operate. Uh we also won't be afraid of of failing and by that I mean recognizing that an opportunity's worth pursuing um as long as we do it fast."
  },
  {
    "task": "Advance key strategic projects",
    "owner": "Peter",
    "deadline": "none",
